task.description:
When a condition uses multitask wrappers, the DataLoader must load precomputed SDF/centerline targets alongside image+label.
Propagation path: condition YAML -> run_experiment.py -> DataConfig(extra_target_keys=...) -> build_train_transforms() inserts LoadAuxiliaryTargetsd -> RandCropByPosNegLabeld includes aux keys in `keys` list -> batch dict has {image, label, sdf, centerline_dist}
LoadAuxiliaryTargetsd already exists in src/minivess/data/multitask_targets.py.
